  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>As a prerequisite to taking this Mystic Art, you must have at least 13 levels in this class</em>. When you first take this Mystic Art, you gain the <strong>Mystic Ring</strong> item.</p><p>You weave a portal to a different destination that you have previously marked. Whenever you take a rest of any type at a location, you can mark the location's name into a ring known as <strong>Mystic Ring</strong>. This ring has one bulk and when equipped, you can create a medium sized portal at a marked location. You can only end concentration on this Art on your turn.</p><p>You can mark up to 3 destinations in your <strong>Mystic Ring</strong>, and in the event you lose the ring, you can spend 5 weeks of downtime crafting a new one.</p>",
